high_descs: Pick up the credit card next to the set of keys.
Turn around to the dresser next to the bed.
anns.task_desc: Turn on the lamp while holding the credit  card.

high_descs: Turn around to face the drawers against the wall.
Pick up the credit card from the top of the drawers.
Go to the left carrying the card and then turn around when you get to the box and go straight to the light brown chest of drawers.
Turn on the small lamp that sits on top of the chest of drawers.
anns.task_desc: While holding a credit card turn on the lamp.

high_descs: Turn around and walk across the room to the dresser.
Pick up the credit card next to the keys.
Turn around and walk past the bed to the desk.
anns.task_desc: Look at a credit card under the light of a desk lamp.
